&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-local-id=&quot;8751bd455e7c&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7847&quot; data-local-id=&quot;46cd5ea001a4&quot;&gt;5+ years of professional software engineering experience, preferably across both frontend and backend features&lt;/p&gt;
