&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;8228&quot; data-local-id=&quot;05990c482b07&quot;&gt;Collaborative and communicative: you work well across teams and functions, and you&#39;re comfortable navigating ambiguity&lt;/p&gt;
